# <type>(<scope>): <subject>
# |<----  Limit subject to 50 characters  ---->|
#
# Explain what and why, not how.
# Wrap at 72 characters for better formatting.
#
# Type: feat, fix, refactor, perf, docs, style, test, chore, ci, build
# Scope: web, orchestrator, db, providers, cli, tauri, sidebar, etc.
#
# Examples:
# feat(web): add file attachment support to chat
# fix(runtime): prevent model timeout on large downloads
# refactor(sidebar): extract conversation item to component
# docs(orchestrator): add API endpoint documentation
# chore(deps): upgrade react to 19.2.0
#
# Blank line after subject, then detailed explanation if needed.
# Use bullet points for multiple related changes.
# Reference issues: Fixes #123, Closes #456
# Include co-authors: Co-authored-by: Name <email@example.com>

